OL,4,CFirms to be forced to justify pay gap
OL,5, The country's biggest public businesses
OL,6, may soon have to publish the gap
OL,7, between the pay of their chief
OL,8, executive and an average worker.
OL,10,FBusiness Secretary Greg Clark says
OL,11,Fdirectors of all companies with more
OL,12,Fthan 250 employees will be required to
OL,13,Fdisclose and explain this difference -
OL,14,Fknown as the "pay ratio".
OL,16,FEqual pay campaigners, business and
OL,17,Finvestor groups welcomed the plan.
OL,19,FBut the TUC said it was "a first step"
OL,20,Fand even tougher rules were needed.
